text: Stefan Baraud (born 6 January 1975) is a Caymanian former cyclist. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Caymanian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Cayman Islands Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
